<item>
            <title>[LU-12866] interop: sanity-hsm test 113 fails with &apos;sizes are different 1048580 1048576&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12866</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test 113 fails with &apos;sizes are different 1048580 1048576&apos; because sanity-hsm test_113 was added to Lustre with tag 2.12.53 on the master branch  and after 2.12.2 on the b2_12 branch. Thus, sanity-hsm test 113 should be skipped for servers with Lustre version less than 2.12.53 and 2.12.3 or however that best works.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logs for failures are at:&lt;br/&gt;
